---
title: Grilled Lemon-Pepper Shrimp Caesar Salad with Avocado and Grilled Croutons
description: Nothing says summer quite like grilled shrimp, a creamy Caesar salad and a pile of fresh veggies! For a delicious twist, we've added grilled lemon to bring layers of vibrant citrusy, smoky flavour.
